OL,4,Cadjudicator over school closures
OL,6,FAs part of this, it will review the
OL,7,Fevidence around the process,
OL,8,Fdecisions, criteria, and other issues
OL,9,Frelating to the five schools involved.
OL,11,FThe Diocese of Portsmouth said it made
OL,12,Fthe referral due to concerns about how
OL,13,Fthe council handled the closures,
OL,14,Fincluding worries about a lack of
OL,15,Ftransparent criteria.
