OL,3,CIsle of Wight Council referred to
OL,4,Cadjudicator over school closures
OL,6,FHe said: "While we are pleased that
OL,7,Fthe cabinet accepted the evidence and
OL,8,Farguments, and voted against the
OL,9,Frecommendation to close Oakfield CofE
OL,10,FPrimary, Brading CofE Primary and
OL,11,FWroxall Primary Schools, we remain
OL,12,Fconcerned about the process, lack of
OL,13,Ftransparent criteria, secure evidence
OL,14,Fand information on which councillors
OL,15,Fbased their decision provided by your
OL,16,Fofficers, to close Arreton St George's
OL,17,FCofE Primary and Cowes Primary School.
