OL,3,CIsle of Wight Council referred to
OL,4,Cadjudicator over school closures
OL,6,F"Senior officers continue to state
OL,7,Fpublicly that the process they have
OL,8,Ffollowed is secure, despite the
OL,9,Fmultiple errors and issues that have
OL,10,Fbeen pointed out not only by us, our
OL,11,Fheadteachers, residents and others,
OL,12,Fbut importantly by members of the
OL,13,Fcouncil's own Corporate Scrutiny
OL,14,FCommittee and clearly understood by
OL,15,Fthe IoW Cabinet in its decision. This
OL,16,Fis a serious concern and impacts on
OL,17,Four future engagement regarding any
OL,18,Fprocess that is proposed.
